{
  "stem": "10588.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Certain things, I don't know, stuck more in my memory than others.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I know nobody was allowed out from the ghetto, in from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I don't remember whether from the ghetto they took me to work or not.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really don't remember, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Dave. ?] I don't-- what I don't remember, I'd rather not say at all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Certain things is like would happened now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Other things, I don't know, maybe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Could we what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very little food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So many children-- you could see children sitting in the street and crying and begging.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- we started-- you know, was no medication.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Living in those unsanitary conditions things become not sanitary, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People started to be sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you saw-- and the worst thing was little children were begging for a piece of bread or for something, children crying.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you couldn't help them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Couldn't help them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I saw my little brother and sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I would have given them my soul that I didn't have much left to give them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that was heartbreaking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was very heartbreaking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[CRYING] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[CRYING] [SOBBING] But they deliberately-- they deliberately did to the [INAUDIBLE] to destroy us, not to put us in such a condition where we couldn't help too much.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And yet, people risked their life to help each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Anyhow--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For example, they would-- children would try to smuggle-- go out from the ghetto and smuggle in some things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like I said, sometimes even if one was a little weaker, you gave a piece of yours.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In that way, you helped each other, try still to, in hiding, to teach the children who didn't have a chance to go to Hebrew schools.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, set up little schools-- still teach them song.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My parents use to say-- [YIDDISH] You have to go continue as normal as we can.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is something that they really picked up from them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In other words, not to give in to despair, but to continue to hope, and to-- [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Always they use to say-- [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, sorry that I'm speaking so much Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But because I remember it that way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, in the middle of the night, approximately a year later, it was November the 17, 1942.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, the ghetto was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this time they informed us we going to be resettled to a family camp with better conditions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're going to have better sanitary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We will be all together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we looked forward to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I didn't-- we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At least, I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Actually from the-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] actually from the-- when we found out, it was too late, [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "David. ?] It was too late.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If people would have known, things would have been-- maybe not that much different, because you nowhere to run.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You have to-- someplace to have to run.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And because they made it so that to murder Jews became legal by the state.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "To save a Jewish child or a Jew was illegal and punishable by death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Therefore, not too many people want to risk to do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And to the credit of some Gentile people, there were still some who risked their life and saved some Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From my family nobody was hidden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I found out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know at the time, though.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I found this out after the Holocaust when certain people survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I asked them, where were you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They start telling the stories.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I even found out I have a girlfriend who was in a Nazi's house in Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she was posing as a Gentile.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She looked blonde and everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she somehow got papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said her heart was breaking when she heard how they talked about the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she had to be quiet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So not everybody the Holocaust started at the same time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not everybody experiences at the same time, because we were not the same people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So everybody's experience is different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, some became Partisans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some were in the resistance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And our upbringing, we didn't want to leave our parents alone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Children didn't want to leave elders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Also, we were told to hurt somebody like us not menschlich, so how can you go kill, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, later on people started to realize that what's happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in the beginning, nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very well kept secret.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the whole idea, because-- excuse me-- for instance before the Holocaust, somebody comes and they wanted you to become-- apostatize.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They knew-- you knew what they wanted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could say yes or no.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
